  "description": "For a speedy, satisfying salad, you'll toss crispy bacon and sweet chilli relish with warm lentils and creamy avocado. To serve, top with feta and pumpkin seeds for crunch. Sizzle, drizzle, done! All Health Hub recipes meet one of these criteria: <600 calories, 3 of your 5/day, or a source of protein.",
